sentences: The group released a single, "The Crown" on 23 July 1983 written by Gary Byrd and Stevie Wonder.
In the UK, it was released on the Motown label, entered the UK Singles Chart on 23 July 1983 at number 21, and rose to a high of number 6; it remained in the chart for 9 weeks.
